use repository pattern.

19
00:01:29,690 --> 00:01:35,090
Let's examine the class diagram for our repository implementation that you can see in the picture.

20
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:41,510
So according to this picture you can see that we will create an interface which name is AI basket repository.

21
00:01:41,510 --> 00:01:47,690
And this interface should be inherited from the basket repository and cached basket repository.

22
00:01:48,140 --> 00:01:53,840
So we will follow the repository pattern which is provide an abstraction layer over the database.

23
